articles.title: Sainz: Bumpy COTA gives Ferrari F1 team-mate Leclerc an advantage - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Carlos Sainz says that he lacks confidence around the bumpy COTA circuit – and that has given his Ferrari team-mate Charles Leclerc an advantage over the Formula 1 US GP weekend.
articles.content:
Leclerc has clearly been ahead of Sainz in Austin, having taken pole for Sundays main race and qualified second in the Saturday shootout, while Sainz was fourth and sixth in the two sessions.
